Freifeld, A. G., Bow, E. J., Sepkowitz, K. A., et al. (2011). Clinical practice guideline for the use of antimicrobial agents in neutropenic patients with cancer: 2010 update by the infectious diseases society of America. Clinical Infectious Diseases, 52(4), e56-e93. La guía de referencia principal de la IDSA para el manejo de la fiebre neutropénica.
